The paper focuses on using deep reinforcement learning to train a robot arm to accomplish a suction task, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of neural networks for training also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of simulation and image processing, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
